00:41:49.507 --> 00:41:52.469  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but fire it up.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1228
00:42:33.759 --> 00:42:35.761  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
