1229
00:42:35.761 --> 00:42:37.263  position:57.62%,start  align:start size:32.86%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You finished</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1230
00:42:35.761 --> 00:42:37.263  position:57.62%,start  align:start size:29.05%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>your work.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1231
00:42:37.263 --> 00:42:39.765  position:51.90%,start  align:start size:29.05%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Now I have</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1232
