1241
00:43:42.495 --> 00:43:45.623  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>over me after all.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1242
00:43:45.623 --> 00:43:47.041  position:50.00%,start  align:start size:40.48%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>That's not true.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1243
00:43:47.041 --> 00:43:49.377  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:25.24%  line:79.29% 
