1249
00:43:55.091 --> 00:43:57.302  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>mine and yours.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1250
00:43:57.302 --> 00:44:00.472  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:57.62%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You say you're my friend.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1251
00:44:00.472 --> 00:44:02.140  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:27.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Prove it.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

